overview: Featured cover girls Baby Nicols and Ginebra Bellucci prefer not to put labels or limits on their relationships. If a man can accept that, all it takes is a bold suggestion to get these beauties in bed together. Milena Ray and Lana Roy, Vicki Chase and Athena Palomino, and Kira Noir and Scarlett Bloom all understand that good things come in threes.
title: Threesome Fantasies 10
